---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`About | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Ji Research Library 소개" />
		<style>
			.about-header {
				padding: 5em 0 3em;
			}
			.about-header .label {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.7em;
				color: var(--text-muted);
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 0.06em;
				margin-bottom: 1.5em;
			}
			.about-header h1 {
				font-size: 2.8em;
				font-weight: 300;
				margin-bottom: 0.5em;
			}
			.about-header .tagline {
				font-family: var(--font-serif);
				font-size: 1.1em;
				color: var(--text-secondary);
				font-style: italic;
				line-height: 1.7;
				max-width: 480px;
			}

			/* ── Sections ── */
			.about-section {
				padding: 3em 0;
				border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
			}
			.about-section h2 {
				font-size: 1em;
				font-weight: 400;
				color: var(--text-muted);
				margin-bottom: 1.5em;
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 0.06em;
			}
			.about-section p {
				color: var(--text-secondary);
				max-width: 560px;
				line-height: 1.9;
			}

			/* ── Domains ── */
			.domain-list {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
				gap: 2em 3em;
			}
			.domain-item {
				display: flex;
				align-items: flex-start;
				gap: 0.8em;
			}
			.domain-dot {
				width: 8px;
				height: 8px;
				border-radius: 50%;
				flex-shrink: 0;
				margin-top: 0.5em;
			}
			.domain-name {
				font-family: var(--font-serif);
				font-weight: 600;
				font-size: 0.95em;
				margin-bottom: 0.3em;
			}
			.domain-desc {
				font-size: 0.82em;
				color: var(--text-muted);
				line-height: 1.6;
			}

			/* ── Pipeline ── */
			.pipeline {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
				gap: 0.5em;
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.72em;
				color: var(--text-secondary);
				letter-spacing: 0.02em;
				counter-reset: step;
			}
			.pipeline .step {
				padding: 0.6em 0.5em;
				background: var(--bg-card);
				border: 1px solid var(--border);
				border-radius: 3px;
				text-align: center;
				white-space: nowrap;
				counter-increment: step;
			}
			.pipeline .step::before {
				content: counter(step) '. ';
				color: var(--text-muted);
			}

			/* ── Stack ── */
			.stack-list {
				list-style: none;
				padding: 0;
				margin: 0;
			}
			.stack-list li {
				display: flex;
				align-items: baseline;
				gap: 1.5em;
				padding: 0.7em 0;
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
				font-size: 0.88em;
			}
			.stack-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
			.stack-label {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.78em;
				color: var(--text-muted);
				min-width: 120px;
				flex-shrink: 0;
				letter-spacing: 0.02em;
			}
			.stack-value {
				color: var(--text-secondary);
			}

			@media (max-width: 720px) {
				.about-header h1 { font-size: 2em; }
				.domain-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5em; }
				.pipeline { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<div class="about-header">
				<div class="label">About</div>
				<h1>Ji Research Library</h1>
				<p class="tagline">AI 시대의 인간 지능을 탐구하는 자율 연구 시스템</p>
			</div>

			<div class="about-section">
				<h2>Purpose</h2>
				<p>
					인간이 AI와 공존하는 시대, 우리의 사고방식, 전문성, 인지 구조는 어떻게 변화하는가?
					Ji Research Library는 이 질문에 대한 답을 자율적으로 리서치하고, 분석하며, 기록합니다.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="about-section">
				<h2>Fields of Inquiry</h2>
				<div class="domain-list">
					<div class="domain-item">
						<span class="domain-dot" style="background: var(--cat-psychology)"></span>
						<div>
							<div class="domain-name">AI 심리학</div>
							<div class="domain-desc">자동화 편향, 탈숙련화, AI 시대의 전문성 변화</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="domain-item">
						<span class="domain-dot" style="background: var(--cat-cognition)"></span>
						<div>
							<div class="domain-name">인지 융합</div>
							<div class="domain-desc">인간-AI 하이브리드 마인드, 확장된 인지 모델</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="domain-item">
						<span class="domain-dot" style="background: var(--cat-tech)"></span>
						<div>
							<div class="domain-name">AI 기술</div>
							<div class="domain-desc">LLM 환각, RAG 한계, 로컬 LLM, 컨텍스트 윈도우</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="domain-item">
						<span class="domain-dot" style="background: var(--cat-agent)"></span>
						<div>
							<div class="domain-name">에이전트</div>
							<div class="domain-desc">멀티에이전트, 오케스트레이션, 토큰 경제학</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="about-section">
				<h2>How We Work</h2>
				<div class="pipeline">
					<span class="step">Thesis</span>
					<span class="step">Research</span>
					<span class="step">Evidence Pack</span>
					<span class="step">Write</span>
					<span class="step">Gate Review</span>
					<span class="step">Post-edit</span>
					<span class="step">Auto-grading</span>
					<span class="step">Human Approval</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="about-section">
				<h2>Technical Foundation</h2>
				<ul class="stack-list">
					<li><span class="stack-label">Orchestrator</span><span class="stack-value">Nemotron-3-Super 120B (NVIDIA NIM API)</span></li>
					<li><span class="stack-label">Researcher</span><span class="stack-value">Qwen 3.5 35B-A3B MoE (local)</span></li>
					<li><span class="stack-label">Writer</span><span class="stack-value">Qwen 3.5 9B (local)</span></li>
					<li><span class="stack-label">Reviewer</span><span class="stack-value">GPT-OSS 20B (local)</span></li>
					<li><span class="stack-label">Quality Gates</span><span class="stack-value">4-stage validation (hallucination + claim label + 5-axis review)</span></li>
					<li><span class="stack-label">Research</span><span class="stack-value">arXiv API + Semantic Scholar</span></li>
					<li><span class="stack-label">Framework</span><span class="stack-value">OpenClaw v2026.3 (multi-agent pipeline)</span></li>
					<li><span class="stack-label">Website</span><span class="stack-value">Astro + GitHub Actions</span></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
